":0.7596959670408412,"textScore":0.7596959670408412,"snippet":"# 2026-04-14 — Orbis Daily Log\n\n## 16:34 UTC — Heartbeat Check\n- sessions_list: GATEWAY TIMEOUT (ws://127.0.0.1:18789)\n- subagents: 1 active (Telegram send task — SIGKILL'd / unknown 'send' cmd)\n- Pipeline: DEGRADED\n- Action: Monitoring. No alert to Khuowgn yet. Will retry next cycle.\n\n## 16:37 UTC — Telegram Delivery Reroute\n- **Issue:** Subagent (c2d275a5) failed — no Telegram tool in subagent runtime\n- **Action:** Spawned planner subagent (63bb70ce) to handle Telegram delivery\n- **Thread binding:** Unavailable via webchat — used run mode instead\n- **Blocker:** cron:e7885813 still needs review/disable; Telegram delivery unstable since 07:18 UTC\n\nSource: memory/2026-04-14.md#L1-L14","source":"memory","citation":"memory/2026-04-14.md#L1-L14","corpus":"memory"},{"id":"e713ee6c72596003c9fb8af319e6481d161b1af515a682bd0d1b4cea91d35fa5","path":"MEMORY.md","startLine":126,"endLine":170,"score":0.7446167255593502,"textScore":0.7446167255593502,"snippet":"| e03e387 | feat(responsive): round 2 hardening across all screen sizes |\n| cbd1fa5 | fix(layout): resolve desktop/narrow-desktop sidebar overlap regression |\n| cbe45c6 | fix(dashboard): align stat card key with BE status_detail value |\n| 4e021c8 | fix: move ViDateInput import to module top level |\n| ebac17c | fix: move ViDateInput import to module top level |\n| d8f3dc5 | docs(openspec): add notification migration execution record |\n\n## Ecosystem Migration (CRITICAL)\n\n```\nBackup: /root/.openclaw/ecosystem-backup-2026-04-11/\n  ecosystem-v4-2026-04-11.tar.gz  (13MB)\n  RESTORE.sh\n  MANIFEST.md\n\nTo activate 34-agent ecosystem:\n  1. cp /root/.openclaw/openclaw2.json /root/.openclaw/openclaw.json\n\nSource: MEMORY.md#L126-L170","source":"memory","citation":"MEMORY.md#L126-L170","corpus":"memory"},{"id":"07cdf349780f84851f44e5ab68761cdbe5f6e4a62559b8fbf3f07e739935bf41","path":"memory/dtlx-context.md","startLine":1,"endLine":46,"score":0.7